<div class="container home-container intro">
  <h2>Monitor and analyze your team's</h2>
  <p>Kyoro is a management tool which let's you track the level of different indicators of your team's wellbeing in terms of work enviromnet. Easy to set up and customize to fit your needs.</p>
</div>

<div class="container home-features">
